item.title: Compiler
item.dc:creator: @SonnyX SonnyX
item.description:
@SonnyX wrote:

delete the @echo off or make an echo Compiled (what did he compiled)
Example for @echo off

cd ../src "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/update/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/items/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/combat/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/io/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/io/packets/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/net/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/util/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/world/mapdata/*.java "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/world/items/*.java pause
example for echo compiled (what)

@echo off cd ../src "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/*.java echo compiled the map rs2 "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/*.java echo compiled the map players "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/update/*.java echo compiled the map player-update "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/items/*.java echo compiled the map player-items "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/players/combat/*.java echo compiled the map player-combat "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/io/*.java echo compiled the map io "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/io/packets/*.java echo compiled the map io-packets "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/net/*.java echo compiled the map net "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/util/*.java echo compiled the map util "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/world/mapdata/*.java echo compiled the map world-mapdata "c:\Program files\Java\jdk1.6.0_11\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/world/items/*.java echo compiled the map world-items pause
